CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 24, 1957, pg. B7 reads: "Clifton DuBois of New York was the outstanding master player in ABA tournament held in Pittsburgh last week."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Clifton DuBois holding two bridge trophies and Master Player plaque, posed in Fort Pitt Hotel for 24th annual American Bridge Association tournament
